Adds the v2 monorepo CI surface called out in docs/blueprint/09-phase-
roadmap.md (Phase 0 exit criterion) and locks the API contract.

Workflows
- .github/workflows/v2-ci.yml: pnpm + turbo for @gv/* (typecheck, build,
  test) plus a control_plane matrix (py3.11/3.12) running ruff lint,
  ruff format check, mypy strict, and pytest with coverage. Path-filtered
  so it doesn't burn minutes on legacy-only PRs. Aggregated through a
  v2-gate job that becomes the required check on branch protection.
- .github/workflows/contract-validation.yml: regenerates the OpenAPI spec,
  diffs against the committed packages/api-client/openapi.json, and fails
  on drift; additionally enforces ErrorEnvelope canonical shape and that
  every non-public route declares 401/403 in its response schema.

Control plane
- ErrorEnvelope/ErrorBody/ErrorDetail Pydantic models replace the inline
  dict envelope so the schema appears in components/schemas (matches
  blueprint 04-api-surface.md). AUTH_ERROR_RESPONSES + COMMON_ERROR_
  RESPONSES wire 401/403/422/429 into every router.
- main.py default_response_class is ORJSONResponse; the previous None
  value made FastAPI assert during openapi() generation.
- app/scripts/dump_openapi.py: deterministic, key-sorted, server-stripped
  spec writer used by `make openapi`, contract-validation.yml, and
  test_openapi_contract.py.
- Ruff cleanup: per-file N815 ignore for app/routes/* (camelCase wire
  models are intentional — they match the api-client codegen). One E501
  reflowed in middleware.py. ruff format applied.

Tests
- tests/test_openapi_contract.py: parity, ErrorEnvelope shape, auth-gate
  coverage, and determinism (build_spec is a pure function).

Docs
- docs/blueprint/08-runbook.md: CI surface table + contract-validation
  failure guidance.
- docs/blueprint/09-phase-roadmap.md: PR6 + PR7 exit criteria checked.

Makefile
- `make openapi` injects placeholder DATABASE_URL/JWT_SIGNING_KEY so it
  works on a fresh checkout.
- `make lint` covers TS typecheck + ruff lint + ruff format check.

Spec ships with 11 paths and 15 schemas; contract gate is GREEN locally.
