+|-------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
+| `.github/workflows/ci.yml`          | Legacy workspace (artifacts/api-server, dashboard). |
+| `.github/workflows/v2-ci.yml`       | v2 monorepo: pnpm/turbo + control plane pytest.   |
